工作内容/职位描述：
1、制定并执行电池系统的测试计划（基本性能测试及产品验证测试）及详细程序；
Develop and implement test (Acceptance/DVT/PVT) plans and detail procedures for battery systems;
2、协同研发工程师一起创建验证测试计划和方法，验证产品性能是否符合客户要求；
Work with design engineers to create design validation test plans and methods to validate performance versus requirements;
3、协同外协测试机构一起搭建及完成外委测试；
Work with contract test vendors during the set up and execution of external testing;
4、测试验证电池系统不同工况、及不同环境下的性能；
Perform battery systems validation under dynamic electrical, and environmental conditions;
5、制定电池系统从样品到量产阶段的测试规范，流程及相关文件；
Develop battery system test specifications, processes and documentation from pilot to mass production;
6、以跨部门的产品测试发展团队核心成员身份的意识，积极参与各项工作；
Participate as a key member of a cross functional product test team;
7、依据实际工作需要制定附加测试流程及规范；
Develop additional test processes and procedures as required;
8、分析测试数据并编写测试报告；
Analyze test data and write test reports;
9、通过对现有产品的测试提出产品改进建议。
Propose countermeasure to better improve existing product under test;
10 上级领导交办的其他工作。
Other tasks assigned by Leaders.
任职资格：
1、电子工程专业或电池、电子、汽车或能源工业相关工作背景，本科及以上学历；
B.S. in Electrical Engineering or equivalent skills from the battery, electronic, automotive or power conversion industry;
2、5年以上电池系统测试经验，熟悉大功率、高电压设备及操作；
5+ years battery testing experience; familiarity with high power, high voltage equipment and operation;
3、熟悉产品开发工作流程；
Experience working within a manufacturing R&D environment is strongly desired;
4、具有组织及文件编写能力；
Organizational and documentation skills required;
5、适应快节奏、结果导向的工作文化，独立工作能强；
Ability to work well in fast-paced team-oriented culture and work independently;
6、工作积极主动，能独立思考并分享；
Ability and willingness to take initiative and offer independent thought;
7、良好的沟通及演示技巧；
Excellent communication and presentation skills required;
8、具有高效管控多项复杂事务的能力；
Ability to effectively manage multiple, competing priorities;
9、能够适应加班或上夜班；
Ability and willingness to work overtime or night duty;
10、英语流利，良好的沟通及演示技巧。
Fluent English, excellent communication and presentation skills required

